			Exceptions	-	Handler.php
			Http 		-	Controllers
							Middleware
							Models
							
	config		-	database	(connection)	
					session
					email
						
	vendor		-	packages
	
	env			-	credentials

	server.php	-	rewrite functionality
			
		
PHP Artisan Commands:
	php artisan serve
	php artisan make:controller UsersController
	php artisan make:component Header
	

Laravel Database Strategy:
	1- Map Database table with Class Name	[DB table = plural , Model Name = Singular]
	2- Define database structure.
	3- Write business logic.
	
Laravel Add migration/ Add new table using code:
	1- make new migration. [php artisan make:migration create_products_table --create=products]
	2- update schema/ migration file.
	3- run migrate. [php artisan migrate --path=database/migrations/2022_02_22_193512_create_products_table.php]
	
